Description
===========

Odp2Beamer4R is a translator form OpenDocument Presentation file into
Beamer Latex Class Presentation scripts (using Treetop ruby library).


Get the project
===============

Odp2Beamer4R is mounted into a Git repository, you can get a clone
with this url:

     git://github.com/neoriddle/odp2beamer4r.git


ToDo List and Pendings
======================

Here is a list of pending features and some detected-reported errors.

- Support 'itemize' and 'enumerate' environments by checking styles.
- Support MathML formulas parsing and conversion to Latex ones.
- Create a task to generate ruby files (Treetop::Runtime classes) from
  Treetop (Grammar definitions) ones.
- Support non ascii characters.

If you detect some error or have SUGGESTIONS or COMMENTS, please BE
FREE TO CONTACT ME to notify me or if you was to make contributions
too.


